{"tid":1298402,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「素人聲明」7.28 將軍澳反送中大遊行","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:37:29.000Z","uid":5809,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc749fd0bf9171609b3706293b2fd1420bd0413","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">7.28 將軍澳反送中大遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我們是一群民間自發，沒有任何政黨背景的將軍澳素人。不撤不散，十八區遍地開花，將軍澳人決定召集728 將軍澳反送中大遊行。</span><br />\n<br />\n日期：7月28日<br />\n遊行路線 (<span style=\"color: red;\">待定，正申請不反對通知書</span>)：寶翠公園 -&gt; 寶林北路 (經將軍澳警署對出) -&gt; 寶寧路 -&gt; 將軍澳政府綜合大樓 -&gt; 坑口文曲里連儂牆 -&gt; 將軍澳單車館公園<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 遊行目的</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n重申五大訴求：<br />\n徹底撤回修例<br />\n收回暴動定義<br />\n撤銷至今對所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n以行政命令解散立法會，立即施實行雙普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有鑒於連日來有傳媒對抗爭者的抹黑，我們尊重新聞自由，但亦在此抗議媒體失實報導。希望傳媒作為具監察力量的第四權，秉持專業精神為市民作持平報導。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 與「將軍澳7.21大遊行」之關係</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">區政聯盟及將軍澳民生關注組 (下稱該政黨)所舉辦之「將軍澳7.21大遊行」，和<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們並沒有任何關連</span></span>。該政黨於7月7日發佈有關「將軍澳7.21大遊行」資訊之前，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並未有與我們溝通，團隊亦毫不知情。</span></span>該政黨曾潛伏於遊行籌備群組內，隱瞞其身份，令團隊對其目的存疑。我們考慮過與其溝通，但礙於該政黨有失誠信，最後決定放棄協調。因此<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們重申，是次「728 將軍澳反送中大遊行」 是民間素人自發，拒絕為任何政黨作宣傳或選舉造勢。我們歡迎任何同路人同行，但請各政黨自重。</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 有關路線安排</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">暫定路線不會途徑TVB。TVB位置遠離市中心，缺乏補給、退場路線。為保障當日遊行人士安全，商討後決定遊行集中於市中心。然而TVB對抗爭者的報導手法偏頗，將軍澳人絕不容忍，抗議傳媒失實報導仍作為主要訴求之一。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次遊行由Hang Ng於7月4日初次提議，到我們一班素人團隊組織起來商討，短短的一星期有賴各個將軍澳群組、連登巴絲的意見。團隊並無政黨支持，亦缺乏經驗，希望大家多多包涵，會繼續聆聽各方聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散，728見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一眾將軍澳人敬上<br />\n2019年7月9日"},{"pid":"8751584921abecbd6f400c0746ec63719bfea262","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:06:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ba496dea198d093fda38b6a9e5b424905cd907a","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:07:22.000Z","msg":"將軍澳人TG GP:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MM9QmE1eavrHI4o0kgcjyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMM9QmE1eavrHI4o0kgcjyA&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=40e0a2d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MM9QmE1eavrHI4o0kgcjyA</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳人7.28遊行TG channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=f45143d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tko728</a>"},{"pid":"9a3463c800d349d231fa0e73f2f7b34d1f9df0c5","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:08:09.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"680ed01cd92ebddba1474888932e9dc32dc23275","tid":1298402,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:08:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36bcaddced5c488b7d4280e448621c952c6d7b3c","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e051c1b8ea3d6e0e9ba136a75bf1f95f809c5dcd","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:10:08.000Z","msg":"歡迎各方提問"},{"pid":"75b7f6970711fe221df9cb343c33a16eff430e34","tid":1298402,"uid":36321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n同時要plan下如何參與盡tvb function"},{"pid":"ff24139e80c47a9a85961d90035f66fcca694bab","tid":1298402,"uid":34415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政黨請自重 面斥不雅"},{"pid":"d78b6f43a1a59b6360596a97280f30268856ac09","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:17:59.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"e5ed3088ef8d67b415e69057f6b2d94d779af724","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"我地不求一步登天，但求百屌成材<br />\n<br />\n連登仔提醒我地唔入tvb係絕對收到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d4667a0a79bee6a163ad296934dbc282d17cd6","tid":1298402,"uid":272652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"推呢個"},{"pid":"d3053cfab3edb30620429ab5326b4059bfa99733","tid":1298402,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:21:12.000Z","msg":"政事台無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13b09521c44ad32196a5c03b5f4e4275c154005","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e37db8f27118d36fe5b4b6dc74b79a1ee3c589e","tid":1298402,"uid":5809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3053cfab3edb30620429ab5326b4059bfa99733","tid":1298402,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:21:12.000Z","msg":"政事台無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df128a05a9f1af207bc547edf7d8fe0b0a8aac2","tid":1298402,"uid":25334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:26:35.000Z","msg":"去時事台再post過啦"},{"pid":"d1db398d4ba7f2ef7d082eaf7f003406a7232aa3","tid":1